---
import ChapterLayout from '../../layouts/ChapterLayout.astro';

const sections = [
  {"id":"intro","label":"Introducere"},
  {"id":"terminologie","label":"Terminologie"},
  {"id":"grade","label":"Grade"},
  {"id":"reprezentari","label":"Reprezentări"},
  {"id":"tipuri","label":"Tipuri Speciale"},
  {"id":"conexitate","label":"Conexitate"},
  {"id":"arbori","label":"Arbori"},
  {"id":"euler-hamilton","label":"Euler & Hamilton"},
  {"id":"orientate","label":"Grafuri Orientate"},
  {"id":"tare-conexitate","label":"Tare Conexitate"},
  {"id":"bfs","label":"BFS"},
  {"id":"dfs","label":"DFS"},
  {"id":"aplicatii","label":"Aplicații"},
  {"id":"bac","label":"Probleme BAC"}
];
---
<ChapterLayout
  title="Teoria Grafurilor"
  subtitle="Capitolul 12 — Grafuri neorientate și orientate, parcurgeri BFS/DFS, conexitate"
  icon="🕸️"
  gradient="linear-gradient(135deg,#1e1b4b 0%,#312e81 50%,#4f46e5 100%)"
  tags={["Grafuri","BFS","DFS","Conexitate","Arbori","Euler","Hamilton"]}
  sections={sections}
  chapterNum={12}
  description="Teoria Grafurilor — grafuri neorientate și orientate, parcurgeri, conexitate"
>

<!-- ─── 1. INTRODUCERE ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="intro">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-purple">🕸️</span>
      <h2>Introducere în Teoria Grafurilor</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="beginner-box">
        <div class="bb-title">🌉 Analogie: Podurile din Königsberg</div>
        <p>Teoria grafurilor s-a născut în 1736, când matematicianul <strong>Leonhard Euler</strong> a studiat o problemă aparent simplă: <em>"Se poate traversa fiecare pod din orașul Königsberg exact o dată și reveni la punctul de plecare?"</em></p>
        <p>Euler a demonstrat că răspunsul este <strong>NU</strong> — și prin aceasta a pus bazele unei întregi ramuri a matematicii.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Königsberg SVG diagram -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:24px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 500 280" width="460" style="max-width:100%;border-radius:12px;background:#f0f4ff;border:1px solid var(--border);">
          <!-- River -->
          <path d="M0,120 Q125,100 250,130 Q375,160 500,140" fill="none" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="40" opacity="0.3"/>
          <path d="M0,160 Q125,140 250,170 Q375,200 500,180" fill="none" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="40" opacity="0.2"/>
          <!-- Islands -->
          <ellipse cx="200" cy="140" rx="60" ry="30" fill="#86efac" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <ellipse cx="350" cy="150" rx="40" ry="22" fill="#86efac" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <!-- Land masses -->
          <rect x="30" y="30" width="440" height="40" rx="8" fill="#fde68a" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.7"/>
          <rect x="30" y="210" width="440" height="40" rx="8" fill="#fde68a" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.7"/>
          <!-- Bridges -->
          <line x1="160" y1="50" x2="170" y2="115" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="240" y1="50" x2="230" y2="115" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="170" y1="165" x2="160" y2="210" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="230" y1="165" x2="240" y2="210" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="258" y1="138" x2="312" y2="145" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="350" y1="128" x2="350" y2="50" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="350" y1="172" x2="350" y2="210" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <!-- Labels -->
          <text x="200" y="145" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="bold" fill="#065f46">Insula A</text>
          <text x="350" y="155" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#065f46">B</text>
          <text x="250" y="25" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#92400e" font-weight="bold">Malul Nord</text>
          <text x="250" y="268" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="#92400e" font-weight="bold">Malul Sud</text>
          <text x="430" y="95" font-size="10" fill="#4338ca" font-weight="bold">7 poduri</text>
        </svg>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;">Reprezentarea schematică a podurilor din Königsberg (1736)</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Grafurile sunt peste tot:</strong> rețele sociale (Facebook, Instagram), hărți GPS, circuite electrice, rețele de calculatoare, biologie moleculară, planificarea proiectelor și multe altele.
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));margin:18px 0;">
        <div class="mini-card"><strong>🌐 Rețele sociale</strong><br><small>Persoane = noduri, Prietenii = muchii</small></div>
        <div class="mini-card"><strong>🗺️ Hărți & GPS</strong><br><small>Intersecții = noduri, Drumuri = muchii</small></div>
        <div class="mini-card"><strong>💻 Internet</strong><br><small>Routere = noduri, Conexiuni = muchii</small></div>
        <div class="mini-card"><strong>🧬 Bioinformatică</strong><br><small>Proteine = noduri, Interacțiuni = muchii</small></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── 2. TERMINOLOGIE ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="terminologie">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-blue">📐</span>
      <h2>Terminologie — Grafuri Neorientate</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Definiție:</strong> Se numește <strong>graf neorientat</strong> o pereche ordonată <code>G = (X, U)</code> unde:
        <ul style="margin:8px 0 0;">
          <li><code>X</code> — mulțime finită și nevidă de <strong>vârfuri</strong> (noduri)</li>
          <li><code>U</code> — mulțime de submulțimi cu 2 elemente din X, numite <strong>muchii</strong></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Example graph SVG -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:20px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 420 220" width="400" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- Edges -->
          <line x1="80" y1="60" x2="200" y2="40" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="80" y1="60" x2="120" y2="160" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="300" y2="80" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="120" y2="160" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="120" y1="160" x2="260" y2="180" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="300" y1="80" x2="260" y2="180" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="300" y1="80" x2="380" y2="140" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <!-- Nodes -->
          <circle cx="80" cy="60" r="20" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="80" y="65" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">1</text>
          <circle cx="200" cy="40" r="20" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="200" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">2</text>
          <circle cx="300" cy="80" r="20" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="300" y="85" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">3</text>
          <circle cx="120" cy="160" r="20" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="120" y="165" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">4</text>
          <circle cx="260" cy="180" r="20" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="260" y="185" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">5</text>
          <circle cx="380" cy="140" r="20" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="380" y="145" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">6</text>
          <!-- Isolated node -->
          <circle cx="50" cy="180" r="20" fill="#e2e8f0" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4"/>
          <text x="50" y="185" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">7</text>
          <text x="50" y="210" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">izolat</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <p><strong>Exemplu:</strong> <code>G = (X, U)</code> cu <code>X = &#123;1,2,3,4,5,6,7&#125;</code> și <code>U = &#123;[1,2],[1,4],[2,3],[2,4],[3,5],[3,6],[4,5]&#125;</code></p>

      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;margin:16px 0;">
        <div class="mini-card">
          <strong>Terminologie</strong>
          <ul style="font-size:13px;margin-top:6px;">
            <li><strong>Vecin</strong> al lui x: orice y cu [x,y] ∈ U</li>
            <li><strong>Adiacente</strong>: 2 vârfuri legate prin muchie</li>
            <li><strong>Incidente</strong>: 2 muchii cu extremitate comună</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <strong>Proprietăți</strong>
          <ul style="font-size:13px;margin-top:6px;">
            <li>Nu există muchie de la un vârf la el însuși</li>
            <li>Între 2 vârfuri: <strong>cel mult o muchie</strong></li>
            <li>Simetrie: [x,y] ∈ U ⟹ [y,x] ∈ U</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── 3. GRADE ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="grade">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-teal">🔢</span>
      <h2>Gradul unui vârf</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Definiție:</strong> <strong>Gradul</strong> unui vârf x, notat <code>d(x)</code>, este numărul de muchii incidente cu x (= numărul de vecini ai lui x).
      </div>

      <!-- Degree example SVG -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:20px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 400 180" width="380" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- Edges from node 3 -->
          <line x1="200" y1="90" x2="80" y2="40" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="90" x2="80" y2="140" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="90" x2="320" y2="40" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="90" x2="320" y2="140" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
          <!-- Extra edges -->
          <line x1="80" y1="40" x2="80" y2="140" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- Center node (degree 4) -->
          <circle cx="200" cy="90" r="24" fill="#ef4444" stroke="#b91c1c" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="200" y="95" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">3</text>
          <text x="200" y="130" text-anchor="middle" fill="#ef4444" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">d(3)=4</text>
          <!-- Other nodes -->
          <circle cx="80" cy="40" r="18" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="80" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">1</text>
          <circle cx="80" cy="140" r="18" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="80" y="145" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">2</text>
          <circle cx="320" cy="40" r="18" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="320" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">4</text>
          <circle cx="320" cy="140" r="18" fill="#6366f1" stroke="#4338ca" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="320" y="145" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">5</text>
          <!-- Degree labels -->
          <text x="80" y="18" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6366f1" font-size="10">d=2</text>
          <text x="80" y="173" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6366f1" font-size="10">d=2</text>
          <text x="320" y="18" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6366f1" font-size="10">d=1</text>
          <text x="320" y="173" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6366f1" font-size="10">d=1</text>
          <text x="320" y="173" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6366f1" font-size="10">d=1</text>
          <!-- Terminal label -->
          <text x="370" y="45" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">terminal</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;margin:16px 0;">
        <div class="mini-card" style="text-align:center;border-left:3px solid #94a3b8;">
          <strong>d(x) = 0</strong><br><small>vârf <em>izolat</em></small>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card" style="text-align:center;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;">
          <strong>d(x) = 1</strong><br><small>vârf <em>terminal</em></small>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card" style="text-align:center;border-left:3px solid #ef4444;">
          <strong>d(x) = n−1</strong><br><small>grad <em>maxim</em></small>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="callout success">
        <strong>Teorema sumei gradelor (Handshaking Lemma):</strong><br>
        Într-un graf neorientat cu <code>m</code> muchii: <strong style="font-size:16px;">∑ d(xᵢ) = 2m</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="callout warning">
        <strong>Consecințe importante:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Suma gradelor = număr par (întotdeauna!)</li>
          <li>Numărul de vârfuri de <strong>grad impar</strong> este întotdeauna <strong>par</strong></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="callout quiz">
        <strong>🧠 Întrebare:</strong> Este posibil ca într-un grup de 5 persoane, fiecare persoană să aibă exact 3 prieteni?<br>
        <details style="margin-top:8px;">
          <summary style="cursor:pointer;color:var(--primary);">Răspuns</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:6px;"><strong>NU.</strong> Suma gradelor ar fi 5 × 3 = 15 (impar), dar suma gradelor trebuie să fie pară (= 2m). Contradicție!</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── 4. REPREZENTĂRI ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="reprezentari">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-green">💾</span>
      <h2>Reprezentarea grafurilor</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <h3>1. Matricea de adiacență</h3>
      <p>Matrice <code>A[n][n]</code> cu <code>A[i][j] = 1</code> dacă există muchie [i,j], altfel <code>0</code>.</p>

      <!-- Adjacency matrix example -->
      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;margin:16px 0;align-items:start;">
        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="180" style="max-width:100%;">
            <line x1="100" y1="30" x2="40" y2="100" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="100" y1="30" x2="160" y2="100" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="40" y1="100" x2="100" y2="170" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="160" y1="100" x2="100" y2="170" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="40" y1="100" x2="160" y2="100" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="100" cy="30" r="18" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="100" y="35" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">1</text>
            <circle cx="40" cy="100" r="18" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="40" y="105" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">2</text>
            <circle cx="160" cy="100" r="18" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="160" y="105" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">3</text>
            <circle cx="100" cy="170" r="18" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="100" y="175" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">4</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <table class="data-table" style="font-size:13px;margin:0 auto;">
            <thead><tr><th></th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><th>1</th><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr>
              <tr><th>2</th><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr>
              <tr><th>3</th><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr>
              <tr><th>4</th><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;text-align:center;">Matricea este simetrică!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Proprietăți ale matricei de adiacență (graf neorientat):</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Simetrică față de diagonala principală</li>
          <li>Diagonala principală = 0 (nu există bucle)</li>
          <li>d(x) = suma elementelor de pe linia x</li>
          <li>Suma totală a elementelor = 2m</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <pre><span class="cm">// Declarare și citire matrice de adiacență</span>
<span class="kw">int</span> A[<span class="nu">101</span>][<span class="nu">101</span>], n, m;

<span class="ty">void</span> <span class="fn">citire</span>() &#123;
    cin >> n >> m;
    <span class="kw">for</span>(<span class="kw">int</span> i = <span class="nu">1</span>; i <= m; i++) &#123;
        <span class="kw">int</span> x, y;
        cin >> x >> y;
        A[x][y] = A[y][x] = <span class="nu">1</span>;  <span class="cm">// simetric!</span>
    &#125;
&#125;</pre>

      <h3 style="margin-top:24px;">2. Lista de muchii</h3>
      <p>Se memorează toate perechile (x, y) care formează muchii.</p>

      <pre><span class="kw">struct</span> <span class="ty">Muchie</span> &#123; <span class="kw">int</span> x, y; &#125;;
<span class="ty">Muchie</span> muchii[<span class="nu">5001</span>];
<span class="kw">int</span> m;   <span class="cm">// numărul de muchii</span>

<span class="cm">// Citire</span>
<span class="kw">for</span>(<span class="kw">int</span> i = <span class="nu">0</span>; i < m; i++)
    cin >> muchii[i].x >> muchii[i].y;</pre>

      <h3 style="margin-top:24px;">3. Liste de adiacență (vecini)</h3>
      <p>Pentru fiecare vârf x, se memorează lista vecinilor săi. <strong>Cea mai eficientă</strong> metodă!</p>

      <pre><span class="pp">#include &lt;vector&gt;</span>
<span class="kw">using namespace</span> std;

vector&lt;<span class="kw">int</span>&gt; adj[<span class="nu">101</span>];  <span class="cm">// adj[x] = vecinii lui x</span>
<span class="kw">int</span> n, m;

<span class="ty">void</span> <span class="fn">citire</span>() &#123;
    cin >> n >> m;
    <span class="kw">for</span>(<span class="kw">int</span> i = <span class="nu">0</span>; i < m; i++) &#123;
        <span class="kw">int</span> x, y;
        cin >> x >> y;
        adj[x].push_back(y);
        adj[y].push_back(x);  <span class="cm">// neorientat → adaugă în ambele</span>
    &#125;
&#125;</pre>

      <h3 style="margin-top:24px;">Comparație</h3>
      <table class="data-table" style="font-size:13px;">
        <thead><tr><th>Criteriu</th><th>Matrice de adiacență</th><th>Lista muchii</th><th>Liste adiacență</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>Memorie</strong></td><td>O(n²)</td><td>O(m)</td><td>O(n + m)</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Verificare muchie</strong></td><td>O(1) ✅</td><td>O(m)</td><td>O(grad)</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Vecini ai lui x</strong></td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(m)</td><td>O(grad(x)) ✅</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Adăugare muchie</strong></td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(1)</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Recomandare</strong></td><td>n ≤ 100</td><td>Rar</td><td><strong>n mare</strong> ✅</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── 5. TIPURI SPECIALE ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="tipuri">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-orange">⭐</span>
      <h2>Tipuri speciale de grafuri</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">

      <h3>Graf complet K<sub>n</sub></h3>
      <p>Oricare două vârfuri sunt adiacente. Are <strong>n(n−1)/2</strong> muchii.</p>

      <div style="text-align:center;margin:16px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 500 140" width="480" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- K3 -->
          <line x1="60" y1="30" x2="30" y2="110" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="60" y1="30" x2="90" y2="110" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="30" y1="110" x2="90" y2="110" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <circle cx="60" cy="30" r="12" fill="#f59e0b"/><circle cx="30" cy="110" r="12" fill="#f59e0b"/><circle cx="90" cy="110" r="12" fill="#f59e0b"/>
          <text x="60" y="135" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="var(--text-muted)" font-weight="bold">K₃</text>

          <!-- K4 -->
          <line x1="190" y1="30" x2="150" y2="110" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="190" y1="30" x2="230" y2="110" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="190" y1="30" x2="190" y2="110" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
