          <circle cx="190" cy="30" r="12" fill="#10b981"/><circle cx="150" cy="110" r="12" fill="#10b981"/><circle cx="230" cy="110" r="12" fill="#10b981"/><circle cx="190" cy="110" r="12" fill="#10b981"/>
          <text x="190" y="135" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="var(--text-muted)" font-weight="bold">K₄</text>

          <!-- K5 -->
          <g transform="translate(350,70)">
            <line x1="0" y1="-50" x2="47" y2="-15" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="-50" x2="29" y2="40" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="-50" x2="-29" y2="40" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="-50" x2="-47" y2="-15" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="47" y1="-15" x2="29" y2="40" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="47" y1="-15" x2="-29" y2="40" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="47" y1="-15" x2="-47" y2="-15" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="29" y1="40" x2="-29" y2="40" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="29" y1="40" x2="-47" y2="-15" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <line x1="-29" y1="40" x2="-47" y2="-15" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <circle cx="0" cy="-50" r="12" fill="#6366f1"/><circle cx="47" cy="-15" r="12" fill="#6366f1"/><circle cx="29" cy="40" r="12" fill="#6366f1"/><circle cx="-29" cy="40" r="12" fill="#6366f1"/><circle cx="-47" cy="-15" r="12" fill="#6366f1"/>
          </g>
          <text x="350" y="135" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="var(--text-muted)" font-weight="bold">K₅ (10 muchii)</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h3>Graf bipartit</h3>
      <p>Vârfurile se pot împărți în două mulțimi A și B, astfel încât orice muchie are o extremitate în A și cealaltă în B.</p>

      <div style="text-align:center;margin:16px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 340 150" width="320" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- Partition A (left) -->
          <rect x="20" y="10" width="100" height="130" rx="8" fill="#ede9fe" stroke="#8b5cf6" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4"/>
          <text x="70" y="28" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#7c3aed" font-weight="bold">A</text>
          <!-- Partition B (right) -->
          <rect x="220" y="10" width="100" height="130" rx="8" fill="#fef3c7" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4"/>
          <text x="270" y="28" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#d97706" font-weight="bold">B</text>
          <!-- Edges -->
          <line x1="70" y1="55" x2="270" y2="55" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="70" y1="55" x2="270" y2="95" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="70" y1="95" x2="270" y2="55" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="70" y1="95" x2="270" y2="125" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="70" y1="125" x2="270" y2="95" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- Nodes A -->
          <circle cx="70" cy="55" r="14" fill="#8b5cf6"/><text x="70" y="59" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">1</text>
          <circle cx="70" cy="95" r="14" fill="#8b5cf6"/><text x="70" y="99" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">2</text>
          <circle cx="70" cy="125" r="14" fill="#8b5cf6"/><text x="70" y="129" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">3</text>
          <!-- Nodes B -->
          <circle cx="270" cy="55" r="14" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="270" y="59" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">4</text>
          <circle cx="270" cy="95" r="14" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="270" y="99" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">5</text>
          <circle cx="270" cy="125" r="14" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="270" y="129" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">6</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h3>Graf regulat</h3>
      <p>Toate vârfurile au același grad.</p>

      <h3 style="margin-top:16px;">Graf nul</h3>
      <p>Mulțimea muchiilor este vidă (toate vârfurile sunt izolate).</p>

      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Numărul total de grafuri neorientate</strong> cu n vârfuri: <strong>2<sup>n(n−1)/2</sup></strong>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin-top:20px;">Graf parțial, Subgraf, Complementar</h3>
      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;margin:14px 0;">
        <div class="mini-card" style="border-top:3px solid #3b82f6;">
          <strong>Graf Parțial</strong><br>
          <small>Aceleași vârfuri, se elimină unele muchii. Sunt 2<sup>m</sup> grafuri parțiale.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card" style="border-top:3px solid #10b981;">
          <strong>Subgraf</strong><br>
          <small>Se elimină vârfuri + muchiile lor incidente. Sunt 2<sup>n</sup>−1 subgrafuri.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card" style="border-top:3px solid #f59e0b;">
          <strong>Complementar</strong><br>
          <small>[x,y] ∈ complementar ⟺ [x,y] ∉ original. Este <strong>unic</strong>.</small>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Complementar diagram -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:16px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 440 130" width="420" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- Original -->
          <text x="75" y="15" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="var(--text-muted)" font-weight="bold">Original G</text>
          <line x1="45" y1="50" x2="105" y2="50" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="45" y1="50" x2="75" y2="110" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="45" cy="50" r="14" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="45" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="bold">1</text>
          <circle cx="105" cy="50" r="14" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="105" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="bold">2</text>
          <circle cx="75" cy="110" r="14" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="75" y="114" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="bold">3</text>
          <!-- Arrow -->
          <text x="180" y="75" text-anchor="middle" font-size="24" fill="var(--text-muted)">→</text>
          <!-- Complementar -->
          <text x="330" y="15" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="var(--text-muted)" font-weight="bold">Complementar Ḡ</text>
          <line x1="360" y1="50" x2="330" y2="110" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="300" cy="50" r="14" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="300" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="bold">1</text>
          <circle cx="360" cy="50" r="14" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="360" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="bold">2</text>
          <circle cx="330" cy="110" r="14" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="330" y="114" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="11" font-weight="bold">3</text>
          <!-- Missing edge from original becomes present -->
          <line x1="300" y1="50" x2="360" y2="50" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="0"/>
          <text x="220" y="125" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="var(--text-muted)">Muchia [2,3] lipsea din G → apare în Ḡ</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── 6. CONEXITATE ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="conexitate">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-green">🔗</span>
      <h2>Conexitate — Lanțuri și Cicluri</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Lanț:</strong> Succesiune de vârfuri <code>L = [x₁, x₂, ..., xₖ]</code> cu proprietatea că oricare 2 consecutive sunt adiacente. Lungimea = k−1 (nr. muchii).<br><br>
        <strong>Ciclu:</strong> Lanț simplu în care primul vârf = ultimul. Minim 3 muchii.
      </div>

      <!-- Chain/Cycle SVG -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:20px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 450 180" width="430" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- Graph edges (all) -->
          <line x1="60" y1="50" x2="150" y2="30" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="150" y1="30" x2="240" y2="50" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="240" y1="50" x2="330" y2="30" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="60" y1="50" x2="90" y2="130" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="150" y1="30" x2="180" y2="130" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="240" y1="50" x2="180" y2="130" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="330" y1="30" x2="360" y2="130" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="90" y1="130" x2="180" y2="130" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="180" y1="130" x2="360" y2="130" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <!-- Highlighted chain [1,2,3,5] -->
          <line x1="60" y1="50" x2="150" y2="30" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="3.5"/>
          <line x1="150" y1="30" x2="240" y2="50" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="3.5"/>
          <line x1="240" y1="50" x2="180" y2="130" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="3.5"/>
          <!-- Nodes -->
          <circle cx="60" cy="50" r="16" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="60" y="55" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">1</text>
          <circle cx="150" cy="30" r="16" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="150" y="35" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">2</text>
          <circle cx="240" cy="50" r="16" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="240" y="55" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">3</text>
          <circle cx="330" cy="30" r="16" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="330" y="35" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">4</text>
          <circle cx="90" cy="130" r="16" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="90" y="135" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">5</text>
          <circle cx="180" cy="130" r="16" fill="#ef4444"/><text x="180" y="135" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">6</text>
          <circle cx="360" cy="130" r="16" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="360" y="135" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">7</text>
          <!-- Label -->
          <text x="225" y="175" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#ef4444" font-weight="bold">Lanț elementar: [1, 2, 3, 6]</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;margin:16px 0;">
        <div class="mini-card">
          <strong>Lanț elementar</strong><br>
          <small>Nu se repetă vârfuri</small>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <strong>Lanț simplu</strong><br>
          <small>Nu se repetă muchii</small>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <strong>Ciclu elementar</strong><br>
          <small>Lanț simplu cu x₁ = xₖ, vârfuri distincte</small>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <strong>Graf aciclic</strong><br>
          <small>Nu conține niciun ciclu</small>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin-top:20px;">Graf conex. Componente conexe</h3>
      <div class="callout success">
        <strong>Definiție:</strong> Un graf este <strong>conex</strong> dacă între oricare două vârfuri există cel puțin un lanț.
      </div>

      <p>O <strong>componentă conexă</strong> = subgraf conex maximal (nu se mai poate adăuga un vârf fără a pierde conexitatea).</p>

      <!-- Connected components SVG -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:20px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 440 140" width="420" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- Component 1 (green) -->
          <rect x="10" y="5" width="150" height="130" rx="10" fill="#dcfce7" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="40" x2="120" y2="40" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="40" x2="80" y2="100" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="120" y1="40" x2="80" y2="100" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="50" cy="40" r="14" fill="#16a34a"/><text x="50" y="44" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">1</text>
          <circle cx="120" cy="40" r="14" fill="#16a34a"/><text x="120" y="44" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">2</text>
          <circle cx="80" cy="100" r="14" fill="#16a34a"/><text x="80" y="104" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">3</text>
          <text x="85" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#16a34a">Comp. 1</text>
          <!-- Component 2 (blue) -->
          <rect x="175" y="5" width="120" height="130" rx="10" fill="#dbeafe" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5"/>
          <line x1="210" y1="50" x2="270" y2="50" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="240" y1="100" x2="210" y2="50" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"/>
          <circle cx="210" cy="50" r="14" fill="#2563eb"/><text x="210" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">4</text>
          <circle cx="270" cy="50" r="14" fill="#2563eb"/><text x="270" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">5</text>
          <circle cx="240" cy="100" r="14" fill="#2563eb"/><text x="240" y="104" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">6</text>
          <text x="235" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#2563eb">Comp. 2</text>
          <!-- Component 3 (single node) -->
          <rect x="310" y="20" width="60" height="60" rx="10" fill="#fef3c7" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5"/>
          <circle cx="340" cy="50" r="14" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="340" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">7</text>
          <text x="340" y="100" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#f59e0b">Comp. 3</text>
          <!-- Component 4 -->
          <rect x="380" y="20" width="55" height="60" rx="10" fill="#fce7f3" stroke="#ec4899" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5"/>
          <circle cx="408" cy="50" r="14" fill="#ec4899"/><text x="408" y="54" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="12" font-weight="bold">8</text>
          <text x="408" y="100" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#ec4899">Comp. 4</text>
        </svg>
        <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Graful are 4 componente conexe → <strong>nu este conex</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout warning">
        <strong>Un graf este conex ⟺ are exact 1 componentă conexă.</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── 7. ARBORI ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="arbori">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-teal">🌲</span>
      <h2>Arbori și Păduri</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Definiție:</strong> Un <strong>arbore</strong> este un graf conex și aciclic.
      </div>

      <!-- Tree SVG -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:20px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 360 200" width="340" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- Edges -->
          <line x1="180" y1="30" x2="100" y2="80" stroke="#0d9488" stroke-width="2.5"/>
          <line x1="180" y1="30" x2="260" y2="80" stroke="#0d9488" stroke-width="2.5"/>
