<!-- ─── 11. BFS ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="bfs">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-blue">🌊</span>
      <h2>Parcurgerea BFS (Breadth-First Search)</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="beginner-box">
        <div class="bb-title">🌊 Analogie: Undă pe apă</div>
        <p>BFS explorează graful <strong>nivel cu nivel</strong>, ca un val care se propagă circular dintr-un punct. Mai întâi vizitezi toți vecinii direcți (la distanță 1), apoi vecinii vecinilor (distanță 2), etc.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Principiu:</strong> Se folosește o <strong>coadă</strong> (queue). Se vizitează vârfurile în ordinea distanței față de sursă.<br>
        <strong>Complexitate:</strong> O(V + E) timp, O(V) memorie auxiliară.
      </div>

      <!-- BFS step-by-step SVG -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:20px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 440 260" width="420" style="max-width:100%;">
          <!-- Graph structure -->
          <line x1="220" y1="40" x2="120" y2="100" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="220" y1="40" x2="320" y2="100" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="120" y1="100" x2="70" y2="180" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="120" y1="100" x2="170" y2="180" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="320" y1="100" x2="270" y2="180" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="320" y1="100" x2="370" y2="180" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="2"/>
          <!-- Level indicators -->
          <rect x="5" y="25" width="50" height="24" rx="4" fill="#dbeafe"/>
          <text x="30" y="41" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#2563eb" font-weight="bold">Nivel 0</text>
          <rect x="5" y="87" width="50" height="24" rx="4" fill="#dcfce7"/>
          <text x="30" y="103" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#16a34a" font-weight="bold">Nivel 1</text>
          <rect x="5" y="167" width="50" height="24" rx="4" fill="#fef3c7"/>
          <text x="30" y="183" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#d97706" font-weight="bold">Nivel 2</text>
          <!-- Nodes colored by level -->
          <circle cx="220" cy="40" r="20" fill="#2563eb"/><text x="220" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">1</text>
          <circle cx="120" cy="100" r="20" fill="#16a34a"/><text x="120" y="105" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">2</text>
          <circle cx="320" cy="100" r="20" fill="#16a34a"/><text x="320" y="105" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">3</text>
          <circle cx="70" cy="180" r="20" fill="#d97706"/><text x="70" y="185" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">4</text>
          <circle cx="170" cy="180" r="20" fill="#d97706"/><text x="170" y="185" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">5</text>
          <circle cx="270" cy="180" r="20" fill="#d97706"/><text x="270" y="185" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">6</text>
          <circle cx="370" cy="180" r="20" fill="#d97706"/><text x="370" y="185" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="bold">7</text>
          <!-- Queue visualization -->
          <rect x="80" y="220" width="280" height="32" rx="6" fill="none" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <text x="220" y="240" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#6366f1" font-weight="bold">Coadă: [1] → [2,3] → [4,5,6,7] → []</text>
          <text x="220" y="258" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="var(--text-muted)">Ordine vizitare: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h3>Implementare C++</h3>
      <pre><span class="pp">#include &lt;queue&gt;</span>
<span class="pp">#include &lt;vector&gt;</span>
<span class="kw">using namespace</span> std;

vector&lt;<span class="kw">int</span>&gt; adj[<span class="nu">101</span>];
<span class="kw">bool</span> vizitat[<span class="nu">101</span>];
<span class="kw">int</span> dist[<span class="nu">101</span>];   <span class="cm">// distanța minimă de la sursă</span>

<span class="ty">void</span> <span class="fn">BFS</span>(<span class="kw">int</span> start) &#123;
    queue&lt;<span class="kw">int</span>&gt; Q;
    vizitat[start] = <span class="kw">true</span>;
    dist[start] = <span class="nu">0</span>;
    Q.push(start);

    <span class="kw">while</span> (!Q.empty()) &#123;
        <span class="kw">int</span> nod = Q.front();
        Q.pop();

        <span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> vecin : adj[nod]) &#123;
            <span class="kw">if</span> (!vizitat[vecin]) &#123;
                vizitat[vecin] = <span class="kw">true</span>;
                dist[vecin] = dist[nod] + <span class="nu">1</span>;
                Q.push(vecin);
            &#125;
        &#125;
    &#125;
&#125;</pre>

      <div class="callout success">
        <strong>Aplicații BFS:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Drumul minim</strong> (graf neponderat) — distanța minimă între 2 noduri</li>
          <li><strong>Componente conexe</strong> — BFS din fiecare nod nevizitat</li>
          <li><strong>Verificare graf bipartit</strong> — colorare pe 2 culori</li>
          <li><strong>Nivel (distanță)</strong> de la un nod sursă la toate celelalte</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── 12. DFS ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="dfs">
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="slide-icon icon-green">🏊</span>
      <h2>Parcurgerea DFS (Depth-First Search)</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body">
      <div class="beginner-box">
        <div class="bb-title">🏊 Analogie: Explorarea unui labirint</div>
        <p>DFS explorează <strong>cât mai adânc</strong> pe o ramură, apoi face <strong>backtracking</strong> și explorează următoarea ramură. Ca un explorator care merge tot înainte pe un coridor până la capăt, apoi se întoarce la ultima bifurcație.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout info">
        <strong>Principiu:</strong> Se folosește <strong>stiva</strong> (sau recursivitate). Se merge cât mai adânc, apoi se revine.<br>
        <strong>Complexitate:</strong> O(V + E) timp, O(V) memorie auxiliară.
      </div>

      <!-- DFS step-by-step SVG -->
      <div style="text-align:center;margin:20px 0;">
