      <h3>1. Sortare Topologică (DAG — graf orientat aciclic)</h3>
      <p>Ordonează nodurile unui graf orientat aciclic astfel încât pentru orice arc (u, v), u apare <strong>înaintea</strong> lui v.</p>

      <div style="text-align:center;margin:16px 0;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 400 100" width="380" style="max-width:100%;">
          <defs>
            <marker id="arr3" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="6" refX="8" refY="3" orient="auto">
              <polygon points="0 0, 8 3, 0 6" fill="#6366f1"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>
          <line x1="55" y1="50" x2="115" y2="50" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arr3)"/>
          <line x1="155" y1="50" x2="215" y2="50" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arr3)"/>
          <line x1="255" y1="50" x2="315" y2="50" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arr3)"/>
          <line x1="55" y1="55" x2="215" y2="55" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arr3)" stroke-dasharray="4"/>
          <circle cx="40" cy="50" r="18" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="40" y="55" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">A</text>
          <circle cx="130" cy="50" r="18" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="130" y="55" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">B</text>
          <circle cx="230" cy="50" r="18" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="230" y="55" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">C</text>
          <circle cx="330" cy="50" r="18" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="330" y="55" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="13" font-weight="bold">D</text>
          <text x="200" y="90" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="var(--text-muted)">Sortare topologică: A → B → C → D</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <pre><span class="cm">// Sortare topologică cu DFS</span>
vector&lt;<span class="kw">int</span>&gt; adj[<span class="nu">101</span>];
<span class="kw">bool</span> vizitat[<span class="nu">101</span>];
stack&lt;<span class="kw">int</span>&gt; rezultat;

<span class="ty">void</span> <span class="fn">DFS_topo</span>(<span class="kw">int</span> nod) &#123;
    vizitat[nod] = <span class="kw">true</span>;
    <span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> vecin : adj[nod])
        <span class="kw">if</span> (!vizitat[vecin])
            <span class="fn">DFS_topo</span>(vecin);
    rezultat.push(nod);  <span class="cm">// adaugă DUPĂ ce a terminat vecinii</span>
&#125;

<span class="cm">// Apel: DFS_topo din fiecare nod nevizitat</span>
<span class="cm">// Apoi citim stiva = ordinea topologică</span></pre>

      <h3 style="margin-top:24px;">2. Dijkstra — Drum minim în graf ponderat</h3>
      <div class="callout info">
        Algoritmul lui <strong>Dijkstra</strong> găsește distanța minimă de la un nod sursă la toate celelalte noduri într-un graf cu <strong>ponderi pozitive</strong>. Complexitate: O((V + E) log V) cu priority_queue.
      </div>

